function Move()
res, gmcparg = CallPlugin("3e7dedbe37e44942dd46d264","gmcpval","char") if (gmcparg ~= "") then luastmt = "full_char_data = " .. gmcparg assert (loadstring (luastmt or "")) () local state = full_char_data["status"]["state"] -- 8 = fighting, 3 = standing, 9=sleeping, 11=resting if state == "8" then return -- if fighting don't launch it. end end
res, gmcparg = CallPlugin("3e7dedbe37e44942dd46d264","gmcpval","room.info") if (gmcparg ~= "") then luastmt = "full_room_data = " .. gmcparg assert (loadstring (luastmt or "")) () ColourNote("yellow", "", "Room: " .. full_room_data["num"])
currentRoom = { roomid = full_room_data["num"], areaid = full_room_data["zone"], name = full_room_data["name"], exits = full_room_data["exits"] } end
for k,v in pairs(WalkRooms) do if currentRoom.roomid == v.RoomId then DoMove(v.WalkForward, v.ActionForward) return end end ColourNote("yellow", "", " ---No match---") end
function DoMove(direction, movedir)
if direction ~= "" then Execute(direction) end
if(Trim(movedir) ~= "" )then Execute(movedir) else ColourNote("Magenta", "", " No direction set.") end end
function OnPluginBroadcast (msg, id, name, text) if (id == '3e7dedbe37e44942dd46d264') then if (text == "char.status") then res, gmcparg = CallPlugin("3e7dedbe37e44942dd46d264","gmcpval","char.status") luastmt = "gmcpdatacharstatus = " .. gmcparg assert (loadstring (luastmt or "")) ()
if (gmcpdatacharstatus ~= "") then char_status = gmcpdatacharstatus
tmpstate = char_status["state"] if tmpstate == "3" then ColourNote("white", "green", LookupState(char_status["state"])) OnDeath() end
end end end end
function LookupState(state)
if state == "3" then return "Ready and Able.........." end
